>% Parallel music
#^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ source.lilypond comment.line.percentage.lilypond
><<
#^^ source.lilypond meta.parallel.lilypond
>  { c4 d e f }
#^^^^ source.lilypond meta.parallel.lilypond
